  "remarks": "Associated with Al-Nusrah Front for the People of the Levant (QDe.137). Committed terrorist attacks in the Syrian Arab Republic. Since 2016 redeployed to Northern Afghanistan to project attacks against Central Asia countries. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link: https://www.interpol.int/en/notice/search/une/6210802. Khan-Shaykhun (53 km south of Idlib, location as of Mar. 2018). Operation zones: Idlib, Aleppo and Khama, Syrian Arab Republic and Faryab, Badghis and Jawzjan Provinces, Afghanistan.",
